==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Wooded
<hw>Wood"ed</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Supplied or covered with wood, or
trees; <as>as, land <ex>wooded</ex> and watered</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The brook escaped from the eye down a deep and <qex>wooded</qex>
dell.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wooden</ent>⟦br⟧
